
Edit name and email
1) git config --global user.name Cenk Ozkay
2) git config --global user.email ocenk@gmail.com

Create new repository locally
1) mkdir helloworld
2) cd helloworld
3) git init
4) touch README

Add or edit new file to remote repository
First connection add is;
- git remote add origin git@github.com:…..

1) git add .
2) git commit -m 'added png'
3) git push


Cloning smo elses repository to local
1) git clone git@github.com:……
